To celebrate the release of Fire
Emblem: Three Houses, new castle
designs are ready for you to use!

Take a look!

If you select a theme, you can preview
it. If you like that theme, tap Yes.

If you would like to change the
theme later, select Upgrade Castle
under Shop, then Change Design.
